\f0\b\fs28 \cf2 Installation Instructions:\cf0 \
\pard\tx1440\tx2880\tx4320\tx5760\tx7200\ql\qnatural

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Drag the "RandomWeb.saver" file to the "System Preferences" panel, or double-click, and follow the directions to install.\
\
