\f0\b \cf2 RANDOMWEB TAB:
\f1\b0 \cf0 \
Displays you current search items. \
\
\pard\tx1440\tx2880\tx4320\tx5760\tx7200\ql\qnatural
\cf5 \ul \ulc5 Digital Photo\cf0 \ulnone : This finds digital photos using a search on camera file names.\
\cf5 \ul \ulc5 iTunes\cf0 \ulnone : This searches using the current iTunes artist. If not playing any music, this item is ignored.\
\
To add a phrase, site or location search item click on the + (plus) button. The choose a type, keyword and minimum size.\
\
The types can be:\
\cf5 \ul \ulc5 Phrase\cf0 \ulnone : Enter in a word or multiple words for a search. To have it do an OR search, separate the words by commas (e.g. earth OR moon -> earth, moon). Otherwise every word is required (e.g. earth moon -> earth AND moon).\
\
\cf5 \ul \ulc5 Site\cf0 \ulnone : Enter in a web site URL. The screensaver will pull images from that site (Results may vary).\
\ul Location\ulnone : Enter in a web page. The screensaver will pull any images off of that page.\
\
